# Core Modules

## Data Retrieval and Processing

- **NewsAPI**: [src/newsapi.py](mdc:src/newsapi.py) - Handles stock data retrieval and news article fetching
- **Sentiment Analysis**: [src/sentiment.py](mdc:src/sentiment.py) - Analyzes sentiment of news articles

## Analysis and Decision-Making

- **Decision Support**: [src/decision.py](mdc:src/decision.py) - Generates trading signals and recommendations
- **Forecasting**: [src/forecasting.py](mdc:src/forecasting.py) - Time series forecasting algorithms

## Machine Learning

- **ML Models**: [src/ml_models.py](mdc:src/ml_models.py) - Random Forest and other ML models for price prediction
- **Model Comparison**: [src/model_comparison.py](mdc:src/model_comparison.py) - Compares different prediction models
- **Deep Learning**: [src/deep_learning.py](mdc:src/deep_learning.py) - Neural network models for advanced forecasting
- **Cloud Models**: [src/cloud_models.py](mdc:src/cloud_models.py) - Integration with cloud-based ML services